<div>
  <div class="banner-header">
    <div class="banner-heading">It's your time to shine.</div>
    <div class="banner-slogan">Connect with other runners in your area!</div>
    <% if user_signed_in? && current_user.first_name != nil %>
      <%= link_to "Find Runners", users_path, class:"btn btn-light"%>
    <% else %>
      <%= link_to "Join now", new_user_registration_path, class:"btn btn-light" %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
<div>
  <div class="homepage-text">
    <h2>Accountability</h2>
    <p>
      The best way to achieve your running goals is to find runners like you! Find runners like youself and hold eachother accountable. Teamwork makes the dream work!
      <br>
      <br>
      <em>“I don’t run to add days to my life, I run to add life to my days.”
          <br>
          – Ronald Rook
      </em>
    </p>
    <img src="https://www.italybyrun.com/draft/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/running_perfect_sport_for_couples.jpg" alt="Two supportive runners">
  </div>
</div>
